Jennifer?

01:03:23.709 --> 01:03:25.426
Father?

01:03:27.087 --> 01:03:28.839
Father!

01:03:35.679 --> 01:03:37.772
Father, answer me!

01:03:40.142 --> 01:03:45.569
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC)

