(MUFFLED CRIES)

01:05:17.364 --> 01:05:19.892
Take me. Please, please.

01:05:19.992 --> 01:05:21.744
Take me.

01:05:25.247 --> 01:05:27.191
Not him. Not him.

01:05:27.291 --> 01:05:28.758
Take me.

